title: Cumin-spiced carrot and sultana salad
ingredients: ['2 teaspoons cumin seeds', '675g carrots, coarsely grated', '75g sultanas', '4 tablespoons freshly squeezed orange juice', '1 tablespoon lemon juice', '4 tablespoons olive oil', 'Maldon sea salt to taste', 'pinch cayenne pepper', '8 tablespoons chopped coriander']
